HEADWORD: Regulize
<hw>Reg"u*lize</hw> <pr>(-l?z)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Old
Chem.)</fld> <def>To reduce to regulus; to separate, as a metal from
extraneous matter; <as>as, to <ex>regulize</ex> antimony</as>.</def>
<mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

